{"word":"ἔλασις","slug":"ἔλασις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἔλασις</b></el> <el>(ἔλᾰσις, εως) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἐλαύνω'><el>ἐλαύνω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a driving away, banishing</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>(<a href='S:subaudi, subaudito'>sub.</a> <el>στρατοῦ</el>), <i>a march, expedition</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>: <i>a procession</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—(<a href='S:subaudi, subaudito'>sub.</a> <el>ἵππου</el>) <i>a riding</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}